    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your flair is shared amongst those who follow your command. When initiative is rolled a number of creatures of your choice equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) within 60 feet of you can use their reaction to take a Bonus Action.</p><p>Some examples might be a Barbarian's Rage, a Monk spending Focus Points for Patient Defense, a Sorcerer converting Sorcery Points, a Bard giving a Bardic Inspiration, or a Wizard casting the Expeditious Retreat spell.</p><p>You cannot use this feature again until you finish a Long Rest or a Respite.</p>",
